latestIgtvVideos.title: One brand Skincare Routine ~ Using Biotique products! 🐝
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Products Used:
°Biotique Bio Honey Gel Cleanser
°Biotique Bio Papaya Scrub Wash
°Biotique Bio Fruit Face Pack
°Dabur Gulabari Premium Rose Water (I didn't use Biotique's toner cause this rose water suits my skin really well) 
°Biotique Bio Dandelion Serum
°Biotique Bio Morning Nectar Skin Moisturiser 
°Oriflame Sunzone 50 SPF (There's a Biotique Morning nectar moisturiser with SPF available too) 
°Biotique Bio Fruit Lip Balm

I've been using these products since the last eight months and they're amazing. These products work really good for normal to dry skin. Also Biotique is affordable and easily available.
Hope you guys liked this video, see you in the next one. Babyee ❤️
